    "body": "This commit adds a new method getPendingTasks to ColumnFamilyStoreMBean, which retrieves the number of tasks that are pending execution. This method is useful for monitoring and controlling the task queue. The method is implemented by returning the number of pending tasks from the memtableLock_.getQueueLength(). This change is part of the issue CASSANDRA-173, which aims to add an atomic int and increment/decrement it whenever we acquire memtableLock. This feature enhances the monitoring and control capabilities of ColumnFamilyStoreMBean."
}

